### Changes in this version (7.5.0) since 7.4.4

#### New features:
 - [2026-04-29:]: increased duration on machine files to reduce check-out frequency
 - [2026-04-29:]: added network:timeout config option and implemented timeout for requests
 - [2026-04-27:]: added support for RI-J as well as RI-JK
 - [2026-02-19:]: added initial support for PySCF density fitting (SCF only for now)
 - [2026-04-22:]: servers now check cert age before refreshing
 - [2026-02-18:]: The digichem version is now printed to the main log file

#### Bugfixes:
 - [2026-04-28:]: added missing doc depends
 - [2026-02-19:]: added workaround for PySCF #3136
 - [2026-02-19:]: fixed duplicate dispersion property in PySCF

#### Documentation changes:
 - [2026-04-28:]: fixed missing link to terminal walkthrough
 - [2026-04-28:]: fixed missing newline

#### Miscellaneous:
 - [2026-04-29:]: update last modified
 - [2026-04-29:]: bumped version to 7.5.0
